Protecting You From Public Health Threats

Our mission is to protect and enhance life

Watch our overview video





 Emergent BioSolutions
Prepare. Prevent. Protect.

We make medical countermeasures that address natural, accidental and intentional public health threats. Our products target biological and chemical threats, as well as emerging infectious diseases. 














